{"tid":2116441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<正視聽> 愛國大媽喺雅蘭唱果首歌係叫《炸機女王》 唔係咩《隆重登場》","createTime":"2020-07-20T07:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T08:16:38.000Z","uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a520f3c399507c4a2778ab29cd1697eb065bc8da","tid":2116441,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"呢首歌本來就係叫《炸機女王》, 但因為派歌果陣撞正911, 驚喺美帝傷口上灑鹽, 所以先自我閹割將首歌改名做《隆重登場》。<br />\n<br />\n但美帝亡我之心不死, 因為驚佢唔開心而改歌名, 無疑係個矮化中華民族嘅行為, 所以請大家將首歌叫返佢正確嘅名, 以突顯我國巾幗戰狼的威武震懾形態<br />\n<br />\n跟我讀三次<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">《炸機女王》<br />\n《炸機女王》<br />\n《炸機女王》</span>"},{"pid":"3133cddcbdec3801b30e733adc62e6f0bb6fedf4","tid":2116441,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"正視聽"},{"pid":"f9ea4384222f22fa6323e209b34993201ce57329","tid":2116441,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06feeb3f2f8b7c00dea1677bf14e631522e3d1c","tid":2116441,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0d51657d3fa263cff7d3cebe9ba6b17a6f4c7ae","tid":2116441,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T08:15:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bf464d5d37b1756c5b5a3f07dc458dded1eb6db","tid":2116441,"uid":165665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T08:16:38.000Z","msg":"onL9"}]}